        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="一-下载相关环境"><a href="#一-下载相关环境" class="headerlink" title="一.下载相关环境"></a>一.下载相关环境</h3><p><a href="https://nodejs.org/zh-cn">Node</a><br><a href="https://git-scm.com/book/zh/v2/%E8%B5%B7%E6%AD%A5-%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85-Git">Git</a></p><h3 id="二-检查环境及下载依赖"><a href="#二-检查环境及下载依赖" class="headerlink" title="二.检查环境及下载依赖"></a>二.检查环境及下载依赖</h3><ul><li><p>检查是否配置完成和版本信息</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">node -v</span><br><span class="line">npm -v</span><br><span class="line">git -v</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>正常显示如下</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">PS D:\user\desktop&gt; node -v</span><br><span class="line">v18.17.1</span><br><span class="line">PS D:\user\desktop&gt; npm -v</span><br><span class="line">9.6.7</span><br><span class="line">PS D:\user\desktop&gt; git -v</span><br><span class="line">git version 2.47.0.windows.1</span><br><span class="line">PS D:\user\desktop&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><h3 id="三-安装hexo"><a href="#三-安装hexo" class="headerlink" title="三.安装hexo"></a>三.安装hexo</h3><ul><li>具体可以参考官方文档<a href="https://hexo.io/zh-cn/">hexo</a><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install -g hexo-cli</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><h3 id="四-初始化博客文件"><a href="#四-初始化博客文件" class="headerlink" title="四.初始化博客文件"></a>四.初始化博客文件</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo init &lt;你的博客文件夹名&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="五-安装npm依赖"><a href="#五-安装npm依赖" class="headerlink" title="五.安装npm依赖"></a>五.安装npm依赖</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> &lt;你的博客文件夹&gt;</span><br><span class="line">npm install</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="六-本地运行博客服务"><a href="#六-本地运行博客服务" class="headerlink" title="六.本地运行博客服务"></a>六.本地运行博客服务</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo clean</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#原先生成的清楚缓存</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">hexo generate</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#生成静态文件</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">hexo server</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#本地运行博客服务</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
